eplyTime":"2019-08-10T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"無大台 不分化 不割蓆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f225d80450d45c52537290262bb15a94d366f4","tid":1416943,"uid":9570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7eb6f28ee80820adeb8496c7337d172092c9330","tid":1416943,"uid":347723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:47:34.000Z","msg":"「咩叫兄弟爬山，各自努力？你就係爬山，人地唔係？」<br />\n<br />\n有人勇武抗爭，亦都有人開嘉年華，<br />\n就當佢地係出來打飛機，但都係想表達意見，<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;A revolution without a dance is not a revolution worth having&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Vendetta<br />\n<br />\n沒有完美嘅抗爭，大家一齊改善！"}]}